<p>Securities offered through strategic capital investments, llc. Member finra/sipc. Disclaimer: private securities offerings may have a long holding period, be illiquid, and contain a high degree of risk. Investors must be able to afford the loss of all of their principal.
<br>No money or other consideration is being solicited, and if sent in response, will not be accepted.
</p>
            </div>
        </div> <!-- ./col -->
    </div> <!-- ./row -->
{% endblock fos_user_content %}
